This is a derivative work. All source files have been substantially
modified from the original FastMember library:

  QuickMember/TypeAccessor.cs
  QuickMember/ObjectAccessor.cs
  QuickMember/ObjectReader.cs
  QuickMember/MemberSet.cs
  QuickMember/CallSiteCache.cs
  QuickMember/TypeHelpers.cs
  QuickMember/OrdinalAttribute.cs

Changes include: performance optimizations (FrozenDictionary, cached
reflection, struct enumerators, span-based operations, IL emission
improvements), modernization to .NET 8/10, new features (IsIndexer,
non-public accessor support, IsKey schema column), namespace rename
from FastMember to QuickMember, and updated project structure.
